Description:
The fearsome Rust King and his Eel Pitt have been defeated, and now it's time for you to delve into his huge treasure.

The riches you find here are a testament to how successful the Rust King was in life.

It's a pity that you can't carry all of them with you, but your space is limited, and you must continue your journey to rescue the princess!
DescriptionAction: You open the most promising chests.
EventName: The treasure of the Rust King
